node.text:
Golden sunsets & majestic wildlife 🌅🦁 Would you like to visit the Serengeti National Park?

If your answer is yes, you can find this stunning park in northern Tanzania. Stretching over 14,700 square meters, the national park is one of the most exciting and famous parks of Africa. Besides this gorgeous lion, you can also meet elephants, giraffes, hippos, buffalos and leopards 🦓🦛

📍Serengeti National Park, Tanzania

🇹🇿 #discoverTanzania with @agpfoto
